data.description: Beautiful four-bedroom two-bath home with an open floor plan. Upgraded kitchen with a fabulous gas stove with extra burner and stainless-steel appliances, plus granite countertops! The master bedroom sits on one side of the house and has a split floor plan from the other bedrooms. The home is fully landscaped in back and front with an auto timer for irrigation! Enjoy the view from your back patio or sitting area that's inviting in backyard. This home also has a nest thermostat and more smart features! The bathrooms are spacious along with every bedroom having walk-in closets. Don't miss this one! It's a beauty.
